RawQuestion: what war did the us lose the most soldiers?
ProcessedQuestion: what war did the us lose the most soldiers

Parses.Sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.09c7w0)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.09c7w0 ns:military.military_combatant.casualties ?y .
?y ns:military.casualties.military_conflict ?x .
?y ns:military.casualties.lower_estimate ?sk0 .
}
ORDER BY DESC(xsd:float(?sk0))
LIMIT 1
